  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0db8\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A child who fell down a hill without a brake was killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Dickwella Police, two 13-year-old school students who were traveling on a bicycle on the steep road crashed into a wall due to the fact that the brakes of the bicycle went off and they could not control the speed.",
        "13-year-old Gayeshan Dinuja Hasmika, the only child of the family, who is studying at Dikwella Vijitha Madhya Maha Vidyalaya, has died in this accident which happened on Dikwella Dodampahala Udadeniya road.",
        "The police say that the accident happened when the mother went with her mother to participate in an extra class and was cycling with her friends on the side roads before the class started.",
        "Although the child who was injured in the accident was immediately admitted to Dikwella Government Hospital, the student who suffered serious head injuries died."
      ],
